<p><b>Non-uniform rational <a href="/wiki/B-spline" title="B-spline">B-spline</a></b> (<b>NURBS</b>) is a mathematical model commonly used in <a href="/wiki/Computer_graphics" title="Computer graphics">computer graphics</a> for generating and representing curves and surfaces which offers great flexibility and precision for handling both analytic and freeform shapes.</p>
