<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nonuniform_rational_B-spline&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<p><br /></p>
<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nonuniform_rational_B-spline&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
